{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1863,"text":"What does it mean to spend our time well?"},{"time":8111,"text":"I spend a lot of my time"},{"time":10463,"text":"thinking about how to spend my time."},{"time":14914,"text":"Probably too much --\nI probably obsess over it."},{"time":17225,"text":"My friends think I do."},{"time":18694,"text":"But I feel like I kind of have to,\nbecause these days,"},{"time":23205,"text":"it feels like little bits of my time\nkind of slip away from me,"},{"time":27110,"text":"and when that happens, it feels like\nparts of my life are slipping away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33086,"text":"Specifically,"},{"time":34261,"text":"it feels like little bits\nof my time get slipped away"},{"time":37134,"text":"to various things like this,"},{"time":38762,"text":"like technology -- I check things."},{"time":41515,"text":"I'll give you an example."},{"time":43586,"text":"If this email shows up --"},{"time":45601,"text":"how many of you have gotten\nan email like this, right?"},{"time":48310,"text":"I've been tagged in a photo."},{"time":51684,"text":"When this appears,"},{"time":53511,"text":"I can't help but click on it right now."},{"time":56946,"text":"Right? Because, like,\nwhat if it's a bad photo?"},{"time":59511,"text":"So I have to click it right now."},{"time":61582,"text":"But I'm not just going\nto click \"See photo,\""},{"time":64053,"text":"what I'm actually going to do\nis spend the next 20 minutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66975,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68176,"text":"But the worst part is that I know\nthis is what's going to happen,"},{"time":72237,"text":"and even knowing\nthat's what's going to happen"},{"time":75706,"text":"doesn't stop me\nfrom doing it again the next time."},{"time":79871,"text":"Or I find myself in a situation like this,"},{"time":84097,"text":"where I check my email\nand I pull down to refresh,"},{"time":89164,"text":"But the thing is that 60 seconds later,"},{"time":92539,"text":"I'll pull down to refresh again."},{"time":98145,"text":"Why am I doing this?"},{"time":99971,"text":"This doesn't make any sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103010,"text":"But I'll give you a hint\nwhy this is happening."},{"time":108357,"text":"What do you think makes\nmore money in the United States"},{"time":113547,"text":"than movies, game parks\nand baseball combined?"},{"time":121742,"text":"Slot machines."},{"time":125195,"text":"How can slot machines make all this money"},{"time":128799,"text":"when we play with such small\namounts of money?"},{"time":134022,"text":"We play with coins."},{"time":135704,"text":"How is this possible?"},{"time":138137,"text":"Well, the thing is ..."},{"time":141490,"text":"my phone is a slot machine."},{"time":145809,"text":"Every time I check my phone,"},{"time":147821,"text":"I'm playing the slot machine to see,"},{"time":150162,"text":"what am I going to get?"},{"time":151925,"text":"What am I going to get?"},{"time":153109,"text":"Every time I check my email,"},{"time":154974,"text":"I'm playing the slot machine,"},{"time":156450,"text":"saying, \"What am I going to get?\""},{"time":158085,"text":"Every time I scroll a news feed,"},{"time":161334,"text":"I'm playing the slot machine to see,"},{"time":163300,"text":"what am I going to get next?"},{"time":166346,"text":"And the thing is that,"},{"time":167521,"text":"again, knowing exactly\nhow this works -- and I'm a designer,"},{"time":170637,"text":"I know exactly how\nthe psychology of this works,"},{"time":172938,"text":"I know exactly what's going on --"},{"time":174817,"text":"but it doesn't leave me with any choice,"},{"time":177083,"text":"I still just get sucked into it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180173,"text":"So what are we going to do?"},{"time":182991,"text":"Because it leaves us\nwith this all-or-nothing relationship"},{"time":186036,"text":"with technology, right?"},{"time":188478,"text":"You're either on,"},{"time":190510,"text":"and you're connected\nand distracted all the time,"},{"time":192909,"text":"or you're off,"},{"time":194783,"text":"but then you're wondering,"},{"time":196061,"text":"am I missing something important?"},{"time":198352,"text":"In other words, you're either distracted"},{"time":201443,"text":"or you have fear of missing out."},{"time":204363,"text":"Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":206822,"text":"So we need to restore choice."},{"time":211942,"text":"We want to have\na relationship with technology"},{"time":214486,"text":"that gives us back choice\nabout how we spend time with it,"},{"time":218716,"text":"and we're going to need\nhelp from designers,"},{"time":222662,"text":"because knowing this stuff doesn't help."},{"time":225491,"text":"We're going to need design help."},{"time":227567,"text":"So what would that look like?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":230656,"text":"So let's take an example that we all face:"},{"time":233487,"text":"chat -- text messaging."},{"time":236089,"text":"So let's say there's two people."},{"time":237690,"text":"Nancy's on the left\nand she's working on a document,"},{"time":240870,"text":"and John's on the right."},{"time":242669,"text":"And John suddenly remembers,"},{"time":244330,"text":"\"I need to ask Nancy\nfor that document before I forget.\""},{"time":250291,"text":"So when he sends her that message,"},{"time":251982,"text":"it blows away her attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255436,"text":"That's what we're doing all the time,\nbulldozing each other's attention,"},{"time":258868,"text":"left and right."},{"time":260306,"text":"And there's serious cost to this,"},{"time":262534,"text":"because every time\nwe interrupt each other,"},{"time":266729,"text":"it takes us about 23 minutes, on average,"},{"time":270000,"text":"to refocus our attention."},{"time":271864,"text":"We actually cycle through\ntwo different projects"},{"time":275236,"text":"before we come back\nto the original thing we were doing."},{"time":278806,"text":"This is Gloria Mark's research\ncombined with Microsoft research,"},{"time":283171,"text":"that showed this."},{"time":284553,"text":"And her research also shows\nthat it actually trains bad habits."},{"time":288532,"text":"The more interruptions we get externally,"},{"time":291482,"text":"it's conditioning and training us\nto interrupt ourselves."},{"time":296303,"text":"We actually self-interrupt\nevery three-and-a-half minutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301176,"text":"This is crazy."},{"time":302351,"text":"So how do we fix this?"},{"time":303676,"text":"Because Nancy and John are in this\nall-or-nothing relationship."},{"time":306950,"text":"Nancy might want to disconnect,"},{"time":308475,"text":"but then she'd be worried:"},{"time":309852,"text":"What if I'm missing something important?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":312296,"text":"Design can fix this problem."},{"time":315311,"text":"Let's say you have\nNancy again on the left,"},{"time":317368,"text":"John on the right."},{"time":318564,"text":"And John remembers,\n\"I need to send Nancy that document.\""},{"time":321279,"text":"Except this time,"},{"time":322532,"text":"Nancy can mark that she's focused."},{"time":324493,"text":"Let's say she drags a slider and says,"},{"time":326485,"text":"\"I want to be focused for 30 minutes,\""},{"time":328432,"text":"so -- bam -- she's focused."},{"time":330771,"text":"Now when John wants to message her,"},{"time":333415,"text":"he can get the thought off of his mind --"},{"time":335566,"text":"because he has a need,\nhe has this thought,"},{"time":337663,"text":"and he needs to dump it out\nbefore he forgets."},{"time":340744,"text":"Except this time,"},{"time":342290,"text":"it holds the messages\nso that Nancy can still focus,"},{"time":346618,"text":"but John can get the thought\noff of his mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350875,"text":"But this only works\nif one last thing is true,"},{"time":354098,"text":"which is that Nancy needs to know\nthat if something is truly important,"},{"time":359564,"text":"John can still interrupt."},{"time":364158,"text":"But instead of having constant\naccidental or mindless interruptions,"},{"time":368295,"text":"we're now only creating\nconscious interruptions,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":372985,"text":"So we're doing two things here."},{"time":374530,"text":"We're creating a new choice\nfor both Nancy and John,"},{"time":378436,"text":"But there's a second, subtle thing\nwe're doing here, too."},{"time":382022,"text":"And it's that we're changing\nthe question we're answering."},{"time":385922,"text":"Instead of the goal of chat being:"},{"time":390056,"text":"\"Let's design it so it's easy\nto send a message\" --"},{"time":393277,"text":"that's the goal of chat,"},{"time":394731,"text":"it should be really easy to send\na message to someone --"},{"time":397808,"text":"we change the goal to something\ndeeper and a human value,"},{"time":400912,"text":"which is: \"Let's create the highest\npossible quality communication"},{"time":405140,"text":"in a relationship between two people."},{"time":408162,"text":"So we upgraded the goal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411832,"text":"Now, do designers\nactually care about this?"},{"time":414667,"text":"Do we want to have conversations\nabout what these deeper human goals are?"},{"time":420538,"text":"Well, I'll tell you one story."},{"time":422321,"text":"A little over a year ago,"},{"time":425415,"text":"I got to help organize a meeting"},{"time":428519,"text":"between some of technology's leading\ndesigners and Thich Nhat Hanh."},{"time":434297,"text":"Thich Nhat Hanh is an international\nspokesperson for mindfulness meditation."},{"time":439158,"text":"And it was the most amazing meeting."},{"time":440933,"text":"You have to imagine -- picture a room --"},{"time":442977,"text":"on one side of the room,\nyou have a bunch of tech geeks;"},{"time":446854,"text":"on the other side of the room,"},{"time":448374,"text":"you have a bunch of long brown robes,\nshaved heads, Buddhist monks."},{"time":454442,"text":"And the questions were about\nthe deepest human values,"},{"time":457697,"text":"like what does the future\nof technology look like"},{"time":460039,"text":"when you're designing\nfor the deepest questions"},{"time":462278,"text":"and the deepest human values?"},{"time":464445,"text":"And our conversation centered\non listening more deeply"},{"time":468159,"text":"to what those values might be."},{"time":470929,"text":"He joked in our conversation"},{"time":472660,"text":"that what if, instead of a spell check,"},{"time":475551,"text":"you had a compassion check,"},{"time":477606,"text":"meaning, you might highlight a word\nthat might be accidentally abrasive --"},{"time":481993,"text":"perceived as abrasive by someone else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484844,"text":"So does this kind of conversation\nhappen in the real world,"},{"time":488839,"text":"not just in these design meetings?"},{"time":491917,"text":"Well, the answer is yes,"},{"time":493116,"text":"and one of my favorites is Couchsurfing."},{"time":496413,"text":"If you didn't know,\nCouchsurfing is a website"},{"time":498890,"text":"that matches people\nwho are looking for a place to stay"},{"time":502799,"text":"with a free couch, from someone\nwho's trying to offer it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506185,"text":"So, great service --"},{"time":507752,"text":"what would their design goal be?"},{"time":509440,"text":"What are you designing\nfor if you work at Couchsurfing?"},{"time":512211,"text":"Well, you would think\nit's to match guests with hosts."},{"time":517589,"text":"Right?"},{"time":518763,"text":"That's a pretty good goal."},{"time":520042,"text":"But that would kind of be like\nour goal with messaging before,"},{"time":522985,"text":"where we're just trying\nto deliver a message."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525374,"text":"So what's the deeper, human goal?"},{"time":528175,"text":"Well, they set their goal"},{"time":530144,"text":"as the need to create lasting,\npositive experiences and relationships"},{"time":535822,"text":"between people who've never met before."},{"time":539343,"text":"And the most amazing thing\nabout this was in 2007,"},{"time":541950,"text":"they introduced a way to measure this,"},{"time":544615,"text":"which is incredible."},{"time":546090,"text":"I'll tell you how it works."},{"time":547421,"text":"For every design goal you have,"},{"time":548992,"text":"you have to have\na corresponding measurement"},{"time":551084,"text":"to know how you're doing --"},{"time":552657,"text":"a way of measuring success."},{"time":554016,"text":"So what they do is,"},{"time":555336,"text":"let's say you take two people who meet up,"},{"time":560120,"text":"and they take the number of days\nthose two people spent together,"},{"time":565010,"text":"and then they estimate how many\nhours were in those days --"},{"time":569136,"text":"how many hours did\nthose two people spend together?"},{"time":571977,"text":"And then after they spend\nthat time together,"},{"time":574136,"text":"they ask both of them:"},{"time":575350,"text":"How positive was your experience?"},{"time":577332,"text":"Did you have a good experience\nwith this person that you met?"},{"time":580952,"text":"And they subtract\nfrom those positive hours"},{"time":584346,"text":"the amount of time\npeople spent on the website,"},{"time":588425,"text":"because that's a cost to people's lives."},{"time":591661,"text":"Why should we value that as success?"},{"time":594066,"text":"And what you were left with"},{"time":595546,"text":"is something they refer to as \"net\norchestrated conviviality,\""},{"time":600311,"text":"or, really, just a net\n\"Good Times\" created."},{"time":603017,"text":"The net hours that would have never\nexisted, had Couchsurfing not existed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608799,"text":"Can you imagine how inspiring it would be\nto come to work every day"},{"time":612783,"text":"and measure your success"},{"time":614300,"text":"in the actual net new contribution\nof hours in people's lives"},{"time":619353,"text":"that are positive,\nthat would have never existed"},{"time":621978,"text":"if you didn't do what you were\nabout to do at work today?"},{"time":625692,"text":"Can you imagine a whole world\nthat worked this way?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":631564,"text":"Can you imagine a social network that --"},{"time":634343,"text":"let's say you care about cooking,"},{"time":635950,"text":"and it measured its success\nin terms of cooking nights organized"},{"time":639005,"text":"and the cooking articles\nthat you were glad you read,"},{"time":641994,"text":"and subtracted from that the articles\nyou weren't glad you read"},{"time":644995,"text":"or the time you spent scrolling\nthat you didn't like?"},{"time":648009,"text":"Imagine a professional social network"},{"time":651529,"text":"that, instead of measuring its success\nin terms of connections created"},{"time":655468,"text":"or messages sent,"},{"time":657081,"text":"instead measured its success in terms\nof the job offers that people got"},{"time":661417,"text":"that they were excited to get."},{"time":664281,"text":"And subtracted the amount of time\npeople spent on the website."},{"time":668643,"text":"Or imagine dating services,"},{"time":671702,"text":"like maybe Tinder or something,"},{"time":673464,"text":"where instead of measuring the number\nof swipes left and right people did,"},{"time":676966,"text":"which is how they measure success today,"},{"time":679074,"text":"instead measured the deep, romantic,\nfulfilling connections people created."},{"time":686613,"text":"Whatever that was for them, by the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691886,"text":"But can you imagine a whole world\nthat worked this way,"},{"time":695138,"text":"that was helping you spend your time well?"},{"time":699009,"text":"Now to do this you also need a new system,"},{"time":701062,"text":"because you're probably thinking,"},{"time":702764,"text":"today's Internet economy --"},{"time":704343,"text":"today's economy in general --"},{"time":705800,"text":"is measured in time spent."},{"time":707094,"text":"The more users you have,"},{"time":709165,"text":"the more usage you have,"},{"time":710567,"text":"the more time people spend,"},{"time":711909,"text":"that's how we measure success."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714419,"text":"But we've solved this problem before."},{"time":717335,"text":"We solved it with organic,"},{"time":719925,"text":"when we said we need\nto value things a different way."},{"time":722883,"text":"We said this is a different kind of food."},{"time":727067,"text":"So we can't compare it\njust based on price;"},{"time":729140,"text":"this is a different category of food."},{"time":731004,"text":"We solved it with Leed Certification,"},{"time":733761,"text":"where we said this\nis a different kind of building"},{"time":737232,"text":"that stood for different values\nof environmental sustainability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742500,"text":"What if we had something\nlike that for technology?"},{"time":747772,"text":"What if we had something\nwhose entire purpose and goal"},{"time":752993,"text":"was to help create net new positive\ncontributions to human life?"},{"time":758971,"text":"And what if we could\nvalue it a different way,"},{"time":762350,"text":"so it would actually work?"},{"time":764634,"text":"Imagine you gave this different\npremium shelf space on app stores."},{"time":768589,"text":"Imagine you had web browsers\nthat helped route you"},{"time":770948,"text":"to these kinds of design products."},{"time":775475,"text":"Can you imagine how exciting it would be\nto live and create that world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":781211,"text":"We can create this world today."},{"time":784978,"text":"Company leaders, all you have to do --"},{"time":787774,"text":"only you can prioritize a new metric,"},{"time":791146,"text":"which is your metric for net positive\ncontribution to human life."},{"time":795573,"text":"And have an honest\nconversation about that."},{"time":797648,"text":"Maybe you're not\ndoing so well to start with,"},{"time":799833,"text":"but let's start that conversation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803035,"text":"Designers, you can redefine success;\nyou can redefine design."},{"time":808754,"text":"Arguably, you have more power\nthan many people in your organization"},{"time":812711,"text":"to create the choices\nthat all of us live by."},{"time":816311,"text":"Maybe like in medicine,"},{"time":817736,"text":"where we have a Hippocratic oath"},{"time":819618,"text":"to recognize the responsibility\nand this higher value"},{"time":823764,"text":"that we have to treat patients."},{"time":825355,"text":"What if designers had something like that,"},{"time":827419,"text":"in terms of this new kind of design?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":830668,"text":"And users, for all of us --"},{"time":832697,"text":"we can demand technology\nthat works this way."},{"time":837176,"text":"Now it may seem hard,"},{"time":838867,"text":"but McDonald's didn't have salads\nuntil the consumer demand was there."},{"time":844529,"text":"Walmart didn't have organic food\nuntil the consumer demand was there."},{"time":848746,"text":"We have to demand\nthis new kind of technology."},{"time":854194,"text":"And we can do that."},{"time":856092,"text":"And doing that"},{"time":857628,"text":"would amount to shifting\nfrom a world that's driven and run"},{"time":861169,"text":"entirely on time spent,"},{"time":865151,"text":"to world that's driven by time well spent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871569,"text":"I want to live in this world,"},{"time":873680,"text":"and I want this conversation to happen."},{"time":876586,"text":"Let's start that conversation now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":879707,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880882,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}